info.name: Chibi Avengers [Tumblr post icons]
info.description: Tumblr 'new post' icons for your dashboard. "Chibi is a Japanese slang word meaning "short person" or "small chimp." The word has gained currency amongst fans of mangled anime. It can be translated as "little," but is not used the same way as chiisana (tiny, small, little in Japanese) but rather cute." *
info.additionalInfo: Icons are from 2012 v.2 buttons and cellcharms (or thereabouts) by CocaKura neé Yuwenicorn. From style 71816 by user 155033.
